UC1 - Create a new wallet
1. Insert RED key AND blue key
2. Create wallet with timestamp in the name. Write only to RED key.
3. Export watch-only wallet to BLUE key
4. Remove RED and BLUE keys

UC2 - Sign a transaction
1. Create unsigned transaction in electrum
2. Insert BLUE key. Copy tx. #Remove BLUE key
3. Insert RED key. Sign tx. Remove RED key. #Encode tx json to QR on-screen.
4. Insert BLUE key. Copy signed tx to BLUE key

UC3 - Run a wallet test
1. Insert RED key. Copy key to memory. Remove RED key. 
2. Sign a message, display via QR. #Validate through some app
3. Insert BLUE key. Copy message. Remove BLUE key

UC4 - Generate a wallet with dice
1.


